            <div class="w-10 sm:w-12 h-10 sm:h-12 bg-white border-2 border-on-background rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3 sm:mb-4">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-lg sm:text-xl">lock_open</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-black font-headline mb-2">No Account Needed</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant">Unlike extract.pics which requires sign-in for bulk use, ImageToURL is 100% free with no signup required for individual image extractions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-tertiary-fixed border-2 border-on-background p-4 sm:p-5 rounded-xl hard-shadow reveal">
            <div class="w-10 sm:w-12 h-10 sm:h-12 bg-white border-2 border-on-background rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3 sm:mb-4">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-lg sm:text-xl">link</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-black font-headline mb-2">Permanent CDN Links</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant">Original website images can disappear if the source site goes down. Our CDN-hosted URLs stay working permanently — your extracted image link never breaks.</p>
