          </div>
          <div class="bg-secondary-container border-2 border-on-background p-4 sm:p-5 rounded-xl hard-shadow reveal">
            <div class="w-10 sm:w-12 h-10 sm:h-12 bg-white border-2 border-on-background rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3 sm:mb-4">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-lg sm:text-xl">palette</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-black font-headline mb-2">Designers & Mood Boards</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant">Save inspiration images from websites and re-host them with stable URLs for Figma boards, Notion pages, or design presentations.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-tertiary-fixed border-2 border-on-background p-4 sm:p-5 rounded-xl hard-shadow reveal">
            <div class="w-10 sm:w-12 h-10 sm:h-12 bg-white border-2 border-on-background rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3 sm:mb-4">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-lg sm:text-xl">description</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-black font-headline mb-2">Documentation & Wikis</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant">Extract images from websites to embed in Confluence, Notion, or GitHub wikis without depending on the original source staying online.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-primary-fixed border-2 border-on-background p-4 sm:p-5 rounded-xl hard-shadow reveal">
            <div class="w-10 sm:w-12 h-10 sm:h-12 bg-white border-2 border-on-background rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-3 sm:mb-4">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-lg sm:text-xl">code</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-black font-headline mb-2">Developers & Web Scrapers</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant">Re-host extracted web images via our API for stable, CDN-accelerated URLs that won't break when the origin server changes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="py-8 sm:py-12">
